{"tid":1232857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：一週內出現兩次大型示威，反映香港市民強大的民意","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:54:56.000Z","uid":34156,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49145d99dd9c332abac932719734d51e17a4cdc8","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASM6J55GJM6JUHBI00D.html?iref=sp_new_news_list_n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fsp%2Farticles%2FASM6J55GJM6JUHBI00D.html%3Firef%3Dsp_new_news_list_n&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPnB8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=eb7ca4f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/sp/articles/ASM6J55GJM6JUHBI00D.html?iref=sp_new_news_list_n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzoN88t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzoN88t.png&h=75bdc104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刑事事件の容疑者を中国本土に引き渡すことを可能にする香港政府の「逃亡犯条例」改正案に反対するデモ行進が１６日、香港中心部であった。主催者の民主派団体「民間人権陣線」によると、参加者は９日のデモの「１０３万人」（警察発表は２４万人）からほぼ倍増し、「２００万人近く」（同３３・８万人）に達した。改正案の審議を無期限延期し、収束を図った香港政府には大きな誤算で、緊迫した局面がなお続きそうだ。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　１６日のデモは１００万～１５０万人が参加したとされる１９８９年の天安門事件に対する抗議デモを上回り、過去最大級のデモとなった。１週間で２度も大規模デモが行われるのは極めて異例で、香港市民の強い民意が示された形だ。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　デモの出発点となった香港島のビクトリア公園には、午後３時（日本時間同４時）の出発前から市民が続々と集結。公園内に入り切れなくなり、デモは予定より約２０分早く始まった。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　大通りの全車線を埋めたデモ隊は、立法会（議会）や政府本部が集まる香港島中心部までの約３キロを行進した。到着地点付近の幹線道路には大勢の人があふれ出し、車両が運行できない状態になっている。デモ行進は同日深夜まで続いた。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　香港政府が発表した条例改正案に対し、民主派は香港の司法の独立を脅かすと反発。乱用されれば経済活動も萎縮させるとして経済界からも懸念が噴出した。"},{"pid":"25b4c51ec32d646cfa011ffeaa4634717c1d31c7","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a781e33b7f03a6a60a0ed2c60ef3ef84ee84d6","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5967a8c11b50f98faf3a07f357cdbc890a58ec95","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dab9eb1bef0be58a2e82b838fda0ce1bbcb3943","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5967a8c11b50f98faf3a07f357cdbc890a58ec95","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91db04610ce8a1585fd8b6398f43a53ad6400ab","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ae58fe35cf1a4e59cc08c33a3c2dd8b2266515","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876b027879b533e75c5fa143fb74b920a244dcd3","tid":1232857,"uid":91721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請林鄭係撤回送中之前<br />\n<br />\n停止推行一切有爭議嘅議案，以表誠意</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩都未贏呀，幾多次遊行都無打飛機呀"},{"pid":"d54073138b3bcca51c16224743f43ea6c32b7057","tid":1232857,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdeaa7f0acb330a0c07fa430e716f6543fc10a31","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e970f81701951d797316838201ea49cfce4c5d","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf4a8bff72823dda277aaff04b96ce95b336b89","tid":1232857,"uid":65218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876b027879b533e75c5fa143fb74b920a244dcd3","tid":1232857,"uid":91721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請林鄭係撤回送中之前<br />\n<br />\n停止推行一切有爭議嘅議案，以表誠意</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩都未贏呀，幾多次遊行都無打飛機呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:44:39.000Z","msg":"無錯, 一日未徹"},{"pid":"b04867d30db758111adad46a0feb09434b182afa","tid":1232857,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf8b7a82a6d4f223af250af5f2464638951d9e0","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bf68c2e5b057075c83360c208cce0563efbed0","tid":1232857,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0b24c36c8bfd0cb1e844d0f0406d8531582e2c","tid":1232857,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭真係好叻，贏曬以往啲特首"},{"pid":"d5b1c6b85a7a57c79c68133d99587433be55c470","tid":1232857,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好比呢啲相流去1帶1路國家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時阻礙國家發展，奶媽一定無國家領導人做"},{"pid":"01ccfa45f5e344114d635f236e79c8c3fc1fa724","tid":1232857,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:54:56.000Z","msg":"反對香港政府&ldquo;逃犯刑事條例&rdquo;修訂法案的抗議遊行將於16日在香港市中心舉行，該法案將允許刑事案件嫌疑人移交給中國內地。 根據組織者的民主團體&ldquo;私人人權前線&rdquo;，參與者在9日從&ldquo;1,030,000人&rdquo;（警方宣布24萬人）幾乎翻了一番，&ldquo;近200萬人&rdquo;（DV 33） 達到80,000）。 香港政府無限期推遲審議提議的修正案，這是一個很大的錯誤，似乎緊張階段將繼續下去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 16日的示威活動超過了1989年天安門事件的抗議示威活動，其中有1至150萬人參加，成為歷史上最大的示威遊行。 每週舉行兩次大型示威活動是非常不尋常的，這表明了香港人的堅強意志。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 公民聚集在香港島的維多利亞公園，這是示威的起點，在下午3點（日本時間下午4點）離開。 我無法進入公園，示威開始比計劃提前約20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 在主要街道的整條車道上行走的示威者遊行約3公里到香港島中心，立法機構（國會）和政府總部聚集在一起。 許多人在抵達點附近的主要道路上淹沒，使得車輛無法運行。 示威遊行持續到同一天的午夜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 民主黨反對威脅香港司法機構的獨立性，反對香港政府宣布的修訂條例。 商界也對此表示擔憂，因為如果濫用經濟活動會導致經濟活動縮小。"}]}